DTSTAMP:20260413T050902Z
DTSTART:20260426T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the NW Perennial Alliance for their Spring Plant Sale! Apr
	il is a great time to buy plants from a select group of local small nurser
	ies and specialty growers who sell an amazing collection of hard-to-find a
	nd old-time favorite perennials\, shrubs\, ferns\, grasses and more. Your 
	support helps these growers thrive and prosper\, and in return they can gr
	ow even more special plants for our gardens! This is a ‘Farmer’s Market St
	yle’ plant sale where you purchase plants directly from each seller. Bring
	 your own small wagon/cart to carry your purchases back to your car. Free 
	and open to the public. Registration not required.  MORE INFO.\n\nhttps://
